            "answer_text": "Shinu is the \u201cnormal\u201d way to say it. However, like all languages, there are \u201csofter\u201d ways of saying it. \u201cNakunaru\u201d is one such word without sounding direct. \u201cShib\u014d suru\u201d is another which is often used for news reportage. think of like die, pass away, or leave us as variations which consider the listeners\u2019 sensibilities. ",
